show.description: Four years after fleeing L.A. in disgrace, Ines returns with her son and a score to settle. At SKY CLUB, she confronts a tattooed escort from her past, binding him to repay a debt. Meanwhile, her enigmatic CEO, Louis, begins a quiet vendetta—one rooted in secrets Ines can’t remember.
